<Body>     	<Title>汕头大火13名女工被熏死 作坊老板已遭拘留</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009/05/22</ReportTime>
	<Content>

		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Object sid="s1">本报</Object><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event></Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">昨日上午</Time>，<Location lid="l2">汕头市潮阳区谷饶镇上堡居委会五片张培雄家庭作坊</Location>发生<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>起火建筑为村民自建的家庭住宅，<Event eid="e3">该<Participant sid="s3">家庭作坊</Participant>主要<Denoter did="d3" type="operation">生产</Denoter><Object oid="o3">耳机</Object>和<Object oid="o3">内衣</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>火灾仅于首层过火，过火面积202平方米。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter>导致</Event><Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">13名女工</Participant>被<Means mid="m5" type="method">毒烟</Means><Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">熏死</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6" oid="o7">15人</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="movement">入</Denoter><Location lid="l6" type="destination">院</Location></Event><Event eid="e7"><Denoter did="d7" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e8">其中<Participant sid="s8">3人</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="stateChange">重伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e9">作坊老板<Participant oid="o9">张培雄</Participant>已被<Denoter did="d9" type="operation">拘留</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">昨日7时26分</Time>，<Participant oid="o10">汕头市公安局110指挥中心</Participant>接到<Denoter did="d10" type="operation">报警</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e11"><Denoter did="d11" type="operation">接报</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s11,s12,s13,s14,s15">汕头市公安消防支队</Participant>先后<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">调集</Denoter>6个大队、8个中队<Object oid="o12">13台消防车</Object>和<Participant oid="o12">154名消防队员</Participant></Event><Event eid="e13"><Denoter did="d13" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l13">火场</Location></Event>扑救，<Event eid="e14">并<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">调集</Denoter>潮阳、潮南区<Participant oid="o14">5支专职消防队</Participant>、<Object oid="o14">9台消防车</Object><Location lid="l14">到现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e15"><Denoter did="d15" type="operation">增援</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">谷饶当地的专职消防队和义务消防队</Participant>于<Time tid="t16" type="relTime">7时40分</Time>首先<Denoter did="d16" type="movement">到达</Denoter><Location lid="l16">现场</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">潮阳消防中队</Participant>也随即<Denoter did="d17" type="movement">到达</Denoter><Location lid="l17">现场</Location></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e18"><Object oid="o18">火灾</Object>于<Time tid="t18" type="relTime">10时05分</Time>被完全<Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e19" type="thoughtevent">据初步<Denoter did="d19" type="perception">统计</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e20"><Location lid="l20">现场</Location>共<Denoter did="d20" type="operation">抢救</Denoter>出<Participant oid="o20">28名被困人员</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e21">其中<Participant sid="s21">13人</Participant><Denoter did="d21" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e22"><Participant sid="s22">3人</Participant><Denoter did="d22" type="stateChange">重伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e23"><Participant oid="o23,o24">伤者</Participant>已被<Denoter did="d23" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l23" type="destination">市区3家医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e24"><Denoter did="d24" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e25"><Object oid="o25">火灾原因</Object>和<Object oid="o25">财产损失</Object>正在<Denoter did="d25" type="operation">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
